- D: Goal Under Specification: Names the announcement but omits how the breakthrough was reached.$e$, hint = $h$Use only the facts in the notes to accomplish the stated goal; eliminate choices that contradict, omit, or go beyond the notes.$h$ WHERE id = '02216183-2086-4eba-831d-0947bfffec07';
