UPDATE questions SET question_text = $q$The student wants to explain how the intervention's design produced its measured gains by pointing to a specific feature of the protocol. Which choice most effectively uses relevant information from the notes to accomplish this goal?$q$, options = $j$[{"id":"A","text":"The structured protocol let students advance their own claims freely before they were ever required to consider or paraphrase a single counterargument, a design that nonetheless coincided with a twelve-point comprehension gain in the treatment classrooms.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"Truth without Goal: Reverses the scripted sequence, which required paraphrasing a counterargument first."},{"id":"B","text":"The structured protocol's scripted paraphrasing prompts coincided with a twelve-point comprehension gain that the researchers now confidently expect will hold across every subject area and grade level taught throughout the district.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"Unwarranted Synthesis: Adds a cross-subject generalization the notes never make."},{"id":"C","text":"The structured protocol, whose scripted prompts required students to paraphrase a counterargument before advancing a claim of their own, coincided with a twelve-point comprehension gain and with teachers' observations of students citing textual evidence during their classroom disagreements.","is_correct":true,"explanation":"Uses only the notes to accomplish the stated goal without overstatement or outside claims."},{"id":"D","text":"After the structured pair-discussion protocols replaced the silent worksheets, the treatment classrooms posted a twelve-point comprehension gain, and teachers observed their students citing textual evidence during disagreements far more frequently than they had before.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"Goal Under Specification: Reports the gain but omits the scripted paraphrasing feature the explanation calls for."}]$j$::jsonb, correct_answer = 'C', explanation = $e$Goal: explain how the intervention's design produced its measured gains by pointing to a specific feature of the protocol.

