• Earlier scholars assumed hieroglyphs were purely symbolic picture writing.
• Champollion's 1822 letter announced a breakthrough in reading Egyptian texts.$s$ WHERE id = '7ecfbd0e-08f7-459a-89af-3baf4181a807';
