- D: Truth without Goal: Treats the debate as resolved when the notes say it continues.$e$, hint = $h$Use only the facts in the notes to accomplish the stated goal; eliminate choices that contradict, omit, or go beyond the notes.$h$, stimulus_text = $s$Agricultural Intensification
• High-yield wheat varieties expanded production in South Asia during the 1960s–70s.
